WEBVTT

00:00:01.001 --> 00:00:02.537
So, I have a friend.

00:00:03.828 --> 00:00:05.924
She's an actress, she's in her 60s.

00:00:06.485 --> 00:00:08.736
She's super bright,

00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:10.175
badass,

00:00:10.199 --> 00:00:12.032
emotionally intelligent.

00:00:12.056 --> 00:00:15.451
And a couple of days before Christmas,
she was at the post office.

00:00:16.258 --> 00:00:19.133
It was really crowded,
as it is around the holidays,

00:00:19.157 --> 00:00:21.580
and she was filling out some forms

00:00:21.604 --> 00:00:23.427
and she was really focused.

00:00:23.451 --> 00:00:27.191
And out of nowhere,
someone moved her out of the way --

00:00:28.041 --> 00:00:32.488
just physically put their hands on her
and moved her out of the way.